-- MIT LICENCE
-- Small raytracer in Scala. (Flat Shading)



- Requirements 
 *Scala 2.8.0

- Install : 
 "make" will do.

After compiled "scala Main" will write out a file called image.ppm in
the current directory with the scene declared  in scene.pov


